WEBVTT

00:00.039 --> 00:02.860
- The plan is solid.
- Okay, I'll do this for you,

00:03.011 --> 00:04.965
and then you'll do something
for me.

00:06.238 --> 00:07.549
Yeah, we'll do it.

00:07.604 --> 00:09.564
Marco: Everybody down
on the ground! [ Gunshot ]

00:09.612 --> 00:11.047
J: Everybody, stay down!

00:11.103 --> 00:12.642
- [ Craig grunts ]
- [ Dana screams ]

00:14.473 --> 00:18.110
I will find out
what you did to her.

00:18.526 --> 00:20.205
Hello?

00:20.253 --> 00:23.756
♪♪

00:24.204 --> 00:25.860
It's my new bank.

00:26.282 --> 00:28.063
- Smurf?
- Yeah.

00:28.312 --> 00:29.499
Holy shit.

00:29.593 --> 00:31.983
With the money in those walls,
we can all do what we want.

00:32.049 --> 00:33.607
She's gonna come after you, Baz.

00:33.655 --> 00:34.788
Don't worry about Smurf.

00:34.836 --> 00:35.858
[ Gunshot ]

00:35.921 --> 00:37.257
It's already done.

00:37.803 --> 00:39.758
I just have to flip the switch.

00:39.928 --> 00:41.623
I was kind of an asshole before.

00:41.671 --> 00:43.615
You stole my shit
and you left me for dead.

00:43.694 --> 00:46.060
I thought we could work it
all out on the way to Vegas.

00:46.123 --> 00:47.257
Vegas?

00:47.421 --> 00:48.603
On me.

00:49.697 --> 00:53.251
♪♪

00:53.299 --> 00:59.259
♪ She stares deeply ♪

00:59.307 --> 01:03.219
♪ Locked inside me ♪

01:03.352 --> 01:06.084
♪ Burnin' brightly ♪

01:06.131 --> 01:09.102
♪♪

01:09.164 --> 01:14.791
♪ One they know
that I cannot take ♪

01:14.909 --> 01:18.354
♪ Waitin' for it all to begin ♪

01:18.495 --> 01:21.526
♪ Every night now, they'll win ♪

01:21.573 --> 01:25.589
♪♪

